{
  "title": "GatewayZ Log-Derived Metrics",
  "uid": "gatewayz-log-metrics",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "description": "High-cardinality log analytics and retroactive log-to-metrics extraction. Combines query-time LogQL (Loki) with pre-aggregated recording rules (Mimir) to visualize provider performance, model usage, error patterns, and streaming health.",
  "tags": [
    "gatewayz",
    "loki",
    "metrics",
    "log-analytics",
    "high-cardinality"
  ],
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": true,
      "icon": "doc",
      "includeVars": true,
      "tags": ["gatewayz", "loki"],
      "targetBlank": false,
      "title": "Log Dashboards",
      "type": "dashboards"
    }
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "environment",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "loki",
          "uid": "grafana_loki"
        },
        "query": {
          "type": 1,
          "label": "environment",
          "stream": "{app=\"gatewayz\"}"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "provider",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "loki",
          "uid": "grafana_loki"
        },
        "query": {
          "type": 1,
          "label": "provider",
          "stream": "{app=\"gatewayz\"}"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".+",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "model",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "loki",
          "uid": "grafana_loki"
        },
        "query": {
          "type": 1,
          "label": "model",
          "stream": "{app=\"gatewayz\"}"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".+",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "level",
        "type": "custom",
        "query": "DEBUG,INFO,WARNING,ERROR,CRITICAL",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".+",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "content": "## GatewayZ — Log-Derived Metrics & High-Cardinality Analytics\nMetrics extracted from structured logs at query time using LogQL. Recording rules aggregate high-cardinality data (provider×model combinations, per-endpoint volumes) into bounded Mimir metrics.\n\n| Section | What It Shows |\n|---------|---------------|\n| Key Metrics | Real-time KPIs: request rate, error rate, active providers, slow requests |\n| Request Performance | Endpoint and method volume, slow request trends, TTFC tracking |\n| Provider Analytics | Per-provider request volume, error rates, top-N ranking |\n| Model Usage | Model selection frequency, error hotspots, usage distribution |\n| Cardinality Aggregation | Provider×Model matrix from recording rules (Mimir) |\n| Anomaly Detection | Current rates vs 1h baselines — spikes trigger when >2× average |",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Key Metrics at a Glance",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Requests / min",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "grafana_loki" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "grafana_loki" },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({app=\"gatewayz\", path=~\".+\"} [1m]))",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 100 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 500 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Error Rate %",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "grafana_loki" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 4 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "grafana_loki" },
          "expr": "100 * sum(count_over_time({app=\"gatewayz\", level=\"ERROR\"} [5m])) / clamp_min(sum(count_over_time({app=\"gatewayz\"} [5m])), 0.001)",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 15 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
